Dialogue: 10,0:01:54.01,0:01:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, that sure was an interesting place.
Dialogue: 10,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? I've had enough of that ship graveyard!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:00.10,0:02:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's not like I wanna live there, \Nbut I wanna visit from time to time.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:03.64,0:02:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it really that nice?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:05.22,0:02:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Rain?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.06,0:02:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,It's... not rain...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:07.94,0:02:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.94,0:02:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No... something's fall—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:14.07,0:02:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:38.34,0:02:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Hang on!! Hold on to the ship!!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:43.10,0:02:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What is it?! What is it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.69,0:02:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream! Yeah, this must be a dream!
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.73,0:02:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Dream?! Goo—
Dialogue: 10,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! More stuff's falling! Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:03.37,0:03:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Turn the rudder! The rudder!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:05.12,0:03:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,No way that'll work in these waves!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:06.83,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy, protect the ship! \NIt can't take this any longer!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:09.00,0:03:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Got it! Hm? Usopp?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.17,0:03:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Cast aside your worries. \NCalmly close your eyes...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:15.88,0:03:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When you open your eyes, \Na quiet morning lies before you...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:23.55,0:03:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Bones!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.93,0:03:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't throw it this way!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:26.97,0:03:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,More stuff's falling!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:28.68,0:03:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Bones!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:29.60,0:03:31.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You idiot! Don't throw it this way!!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:35.90,0:03:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the heck did a ship fall from the sky?!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:39.36,0:03:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,How weird...
Dialogue: 10,0:03:40.90,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man, the Grand Line is a crazy place!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:46.24,0:03:49.25,Default,,0,0,0,,First, we see a ship graveyard inside a rainbow mist,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.25,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and then a ship falls from the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:50.75,0:03:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:51.91,0:03:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.37,0:03:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What're we gonna do?! Our Log Pose is broken!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:56.75,0:03:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's stuck pointing upwards.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:58.60,0:04:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it. It was updated by an island with stronger magnetism.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.68,0:04:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:04.30,0:04:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If the Log Pose needle is pointing upwards,
Dialogue: 10,0:04:06.80,0:04:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that means the log has been caught by the sky island.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sky island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:12.52,0:04:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.77,0:04:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A floating island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:15.81,0:04:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Did that ship and those bones fall from there?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:19.23,0:04:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But I can't see anything like an island in the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:22.61,0:04:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:25.07,0:04:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,To be precise, a sea is what's floating.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:28.24,0:04:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A sea?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.50,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting more and more confused.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:33.50,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yaay! \NThere's a sea with an island floating in the sky?!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.38,0:04:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Let's head there right away!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.92,0:04:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, guys! Turn the rudder upwards!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.59,0:04:45.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Upwards rudder full!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:46.76,0:04:49.89,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, you can't turn upwards, Captain.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:50.47,0:04:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,To be honest, I've never seen the sky island, \Nnor do I know much about it.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:56.14,0:05:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! It's impossible for an \Nisland or a sea to float in the air!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.40,0:05:02.57,Default,,0,0,0,,So the Log Pose really must be broken.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:02.57,0:05:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, Navigator.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:04.65,0:05:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Our concern right now should not be the Log Pose, \Nit should be how we get to the sky.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.79,0:05:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter what weird situations \Nthis ship gets caught up in,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.38,0:05:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,or how panicked we get,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:20.25,0:05:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,we must not doubt the Log Pose. \NThis is an ironclad rule.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:24.58,0:05:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What we should doubt is rather \Nthe common sense in our heads.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.47,0:05:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's definitely an island where it's pointing.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:42.98,0:05:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that woman doing, opening the coffin?!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.37,0:05:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you learn something from that?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:51.87,0:05:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:52.66,0:05:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got strange interests!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty woman and the dead, \Nnow that's an interesting combination.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:59.88,0:06:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Where's Luffy?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.84,0:06:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Jump, Luffy!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:02.75,0:06:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:03.84,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What're they doing now?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.38,0:06:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Exploration, they said.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:08.84,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, restoration complete!
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.85,0:06:14.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The holes here are man-made.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.64,0:06:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... then this guy was \Npierced there and died, huh?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:18.45,0:06:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No, these are indications of medical treatment.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.40,0:06:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's craterization, isn't it, Doctor?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.90,0:06:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, in the past, they made holes in the \Nskull in order to constrain a brain tumor.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,But that's a medical technique from very long ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:32.28,0:06:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. \NIt's been at least 200 years since he died.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:39.21,0:06:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,He was in his early 30s.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.34,0:06:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell sick while traveling on the sea and died.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:52.05,0:06:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason his teeth remained in good \Ncondition compared to his other bones is...
Dialogue: 10,0:06:58.43,0:07:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...because tar was rubbed onto them.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:00.39,0:07:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This custom is characteristic of \Nsome areas in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.36,0:07:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,So considering history, that was a ship \Nfor an exploration party from the past.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:11.78,0:07:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it is. The "St. Briss" of Briss, \Na kingdom in the South Blue.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.97,0:07:18.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It set sail 208 years ago.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:19.28,0:07:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the same ship as the one that fell.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:21.04,0:07:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Come to think of it, it had a symbol like that.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:23.71,0:07:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This ship probably wandered in \Nthe sky for at least 200 years.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.21,0:07:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You can find out all that \Njust by looking at bones?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Dead people may not speak, \Nbut they do hold information.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:35.39,0:07:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,If the ship was for an exploration party,
Dialogue: 10,0:07:37.10,0:07:40.43,Default,,0,0,0,,it should still hold various records and evidence.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:40.43,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... but the ship sank in the sea...
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.32,0:07:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What're you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:43.85,0:07:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Luffy! Hang in there!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:46.22,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Help me!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:49.40,0:07:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:51.70,0:07:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:54.49,0:07:57.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I found something incredible! Look at this!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.26,0:07:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.79,0:08:02.33,Default,,0,0,0,,A map of the sky island?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.64,0:08:03.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Skypiea...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:03.92,0:08:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,See? See?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:05.04,0:08:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Does this mean that there's \Nreally an island in the sky?!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.63,0:08:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:11.30,0:08:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! The sky island exists! \NIt's a dream island!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.18,0:08:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We can go to a dream island!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.76,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,A dream island!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get so carried away! \NThis only means it might be possible.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:23.44,0:08:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,There're tons of fake maps out there.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.98,0:08:31.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... Sorry! It exists! I'm sure it exists, but...
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.70,0:08:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Luffy! I'm telling you,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.32,0:08:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Uhm, Nami, please treat the ship with care.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.74,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we don't know how to get there!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.78,0:08:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the navigator! Figure something out!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:38.87,0:08:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,There are some things you can't just "figure out," you know!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.45,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}'s cute when she's angry, too.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:42.04,0:08:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care! We're going to the sky!!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:45.33,0:08:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is getting us nowhere.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.88,0:08:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, we can't move \Nthe ship forward this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:08:49.50,0:08:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What we need now is information, as Robin said.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.17,0:08:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If a huge ship like that really went to the sky,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.05,0:08:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,then there's definitely a way \Nfor this ship to go there as well.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:59.35,0:09:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's somehow pull out whatever \Nrecords remain in that ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.14,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,But the ship has completely sunk.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:07.65,0:09:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If it sank, then we'll salvage it!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:10.28,0:09:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.73,0:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,As if we could!!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:13.82,0:09:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's salvage?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,It means to pull up a sunken ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:17.86,0:09:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But it won't work, since that ship is too big.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well... \NYou really make us do reckless things.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.17,0:09:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Er...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:32.96,0:09:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Nami-{\i1}san{\i0}! I'll be sure to find a clue to the sky!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.89,0:09:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Worry not, there are no defects in my design.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.69,0:09:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I wish you... good luck!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:57.07,0:09:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy...
Dialogue: 10,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Chopper. Everyone, please respond.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:01.86,0:10:04.91,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Luffy. \NThere're tons of monsters down here, over.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:04.91,0:10:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this a giant sea snakes' nest?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:07.25,0:10:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This is Sanji. Whoa! They looked this way!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:09.67,0:10:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.63,0:10:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They'll survive. Don't worry!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.72,0:10:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Chopper, hold the brake tight, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.26,0:10:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.97,0:10:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Phew... I'm glad I didn't go.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:23.43,0:10:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:24.56,0:10:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.48,0:10:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:33.98,0:10:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.48,0:10:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:39.66,0:10:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.14,0:10:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage, salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:48.25,0:10:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Company, halt!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Salvage...
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.17,0:10:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:55.96,0:10:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this the area where a ship sank?!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.84,0:11:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir! Boss!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.22,0:11:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,By boss... they mean me!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.77,0:11:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to salvage the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:08.64,0:11:11.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The sunken ship belongs to me, \Nthe king of salvagers
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.65,0:11:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and the boss of the Masira Pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.82,0:11:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy... weirdoes at a time like this...
Dialogue: 10,0:11:22.24,0:11:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you! What're you guys doing there?! \NThis is my turf!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.95,0:11:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Your turf?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:28.41,0:11:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. Every ship that sinks \Nin this territory belongs to me.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:33.63,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't touched anything \Nthat's mine, have you, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.71,0:11:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like... he's going to salvage the ship.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.05,0:11:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what it sounds like.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.38,0:11:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Then what? Doesn't this work for us?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:44.93,0:11:50.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit mumbling! Answer my question!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.77,0:11:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me! Can I ask you a question?!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.40,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me a question?! \NThat's fine. Ask me anything!
Dialogue: 10,0:11:57.57,0:12:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like you're going to salvage the ship. \NIs that right?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:00.36,0:12:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:04.28,0:12:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey... Do you find me that "monkeyful"?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:07.82,0:12:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkeyful?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:08.74,0:12:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That means "handsome." Do you think I am?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:12.21,0:12:13.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, come on, stop it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,But there isn't such a word, is there?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.34,0:12:21.26,Default,,0,0,0,,So, are you gonna salvage it?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:21.26,0:12:25.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! \NIf there's a sunken ship in front of me,
Dialogue: 10,0:12:25.05,0:12:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll salvage it! I'm that kind of a man!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:27.39,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's on the water, I'll sink it and salvage it! \NI'm that kind of a man!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:30.72,0:12:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no ship that we can't salvage!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:34.31,0:12:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... is it okay if we watch you do it?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:37.77,0:12:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Oh, I see, is salvaging work new to you?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.15,0:12:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, go ahead and observe it!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.69,0:12:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! \NLet's see how things go for now, everyone.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.95,0:12:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Be... Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:53.50,0:12:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! There's trouble!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.17,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.92,0:12:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The members who went into \Nthe sea to set the cradle are...!
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.92,0:13:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they get hurt by Sea Kings?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:01.05,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... it looks like they \Nwere beaten up by someone.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:04.26,0:13:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Are you saying there's \Nsomeone down there in the sea?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.55,0:13:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those idiots...!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:09.14,0:13:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.60,0:13:13.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then... Hey, you guys!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah... well...
Dialogue: 10,0:13:14.73,0:13:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in the sea! Be careful!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:17.77,0:13:19.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Er... O-Okay!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Good thing he's an idiot.{\i0}
Dialogue: 10,0:13:20.69,0:13:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys! Hurry up and set the cradle!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.61,0:13:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's start salvaging!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:27.11,0:13:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.44,0:14:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,He's waving to us... \NDon't let him notice the air supply, Usopp.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:03.11,0:14:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys, imagine that they're pumpkins!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.20,0:14:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get nervous... just because \Npeople are watching, okay?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.08,0:14:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Drop the cradle!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.25,0:14:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:22.54,0:14:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch out for the mysterious enemy!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:24.21,0:14:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if they're doing this \Nout of pride or something.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:30.47,0:14:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,They're trying to give us a show, I guess...
Dialogue: 10,0:14:33.71,0:14:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Get moving!
Dialogue: 10,0:14:35.89,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:06.94,0:16:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 10,0:16:07.61,0:16:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.69,0:16:09.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Look!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:41.14,0:16:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Cradle set, confirmed!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:45.10,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:46.36,0:16:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that monkey?! What's that monkey for?!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.54,0:17:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this one?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.08,0:17:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a discerning eye.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:08.29,0:17:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right. This is no ordinary prow.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:12.55,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Launch Barco-hunter!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:16.51,0:17:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:28.11,0:17:29.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.69,0:17:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow! Amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:35.20,0:17:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really amazing!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:36.49,0:17:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What is?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,40 meters to the target!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:42.16,0:17:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,30 meters!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.41,0:17:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,20... 10...!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:50.00,0:17:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Barco-hunter joint... completed!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.71,0:17:57.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, then! I'll start blowing air!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:57.05,0:18:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:00.05,0:18:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What? No way...
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he going to breathe into \Nthat and lift the ship up?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That's crazy!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.29,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Air?!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.88,Default,,0,0,0,,The ship's body has risen!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.34,0:18:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Now! Pull it up!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:42.51,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:45.56,0:18:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Send more air! On the double!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.72,0:18:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! The crew that's in the water...!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:02.62,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?! What happened, guys?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:07.20,0:19:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone in the ship!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:16.71,0:19:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,How dare they hurt my guys?! \NWho the hell are they?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.02,0:19:30.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we're not taking pictures or anything, so...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.94,0:19:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:32.19,0:19:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, he posed for us to take pictures...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:34.02,0:19:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss! Help!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.15,0:19:41.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming! \NKeep on working on the salvaging operation!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.53,0:19:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Aye, aye, sir!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.55,0:20:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Monkey punch!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:08.18,0:20:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's coming up...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:14.27,0:20:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,See? We're fine without the barrel.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:17.16,0:20:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's amazing that they pumped in this much air.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.60,0:20:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But who is trying to salvage this ship?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:24.53,0:20:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Something might have happened \Nto Nami-{\i1}san{\i0} and Robin-{\i1}chan{\i0}.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.99,0:20:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been calling them, but no response!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.66,0:20:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you, invading my turf?!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:36.17,0:20:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.21,0:20:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's a monkey.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.59,0:20:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Am I that monkeyful?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.92,0:20:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're an imitation monkey.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.60,0:20:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What kind of conversation is that?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.60,0:20:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:50.39,0:20:51.60,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who are you?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.60,0:20:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... What can I say?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:54.27,0:20:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you really think so? You have a good eye!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:57.77,0:20:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:03.95,0:21:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, underneath the ship...
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.53,0:21:11.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah... there's something down there.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:14.87,0:21:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! You guys came from the East Blue, huh?!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:19.17,0:21:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. \NBut really, you look just like a monkey!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:23.68,0:21:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit complimenting me!
Dialogue: 10,0:21:46.82,0:21:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?! What is this thing?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:10.61,0:23:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahhh! It's a turtle!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:12.28,0:23:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the sea! Of course we'll see turtles!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:14.41,0:23:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Zoro! Sanji!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:16.20,0:23:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up and be quiet!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:17.95,0:23:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A galleon fell, and then a \Nweird monkey shows up!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:22.71,0:23:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?! It's become pitch dark!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:24.67,0:23:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's next?!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:26.30,0:23:27.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 10,0:23:27.88,0:23:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Monsters Appear! \NDon't Mess with the Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 10,0:23:31.18,0:23:33.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
