Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.71,0:22:13.31,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,1000)\fsp-1\blur0.4}The future that I once saw is now starting to take shape
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.19,0:22:28.61,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur0.4}There are days where I almost lose to myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.61,0:22:30.70,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur0.4}When that happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.70,0:22:35.62,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,200)\blur0.4}there was someplace warm I could go
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.04,0:22:43.09,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,100)\blur0.4}The friends I took pride in always, without fail,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.09,0:22:53.60,ED9-English,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,1000)\blur0.4}pushed me onwards, didn't they?
